orm duration-300\",\"unoptimized\":true}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\",\"children\":\"2026 羥基酪醇與腦健康：橄欖油預防認知衰退的科學實踐\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\",\"children\":[9,\" 分鐘閱讀\"]}]]}]]}]}]]}]]}]}]\n24:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"💬\"}],\" 常見問題\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"details\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\",\"children\":\"2026 年橄欖油市場的品質標準有什麼新趨勢？\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\",\"children\":\"▾\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\",\"children\":\"2026 年橄欖油市場出現三個重要品質趨勢：(1) 多酚量化標示普及——越來越多品牌開始在標籤上主動標示總酚含量（TPC）或羥基酪醇含量；(2) QR Code 產品溯源——掃碼即可查看特定批次的採收日期、莊園位置和第三方 CoA 報告；(3) 早摘油（Early Harvest）市場擴大——消費者對高多酚意識提升，帶動早摘橄欖油的溢價市場成長。IOC 也在 2024 年更新了感官評鑑規範，強化了對缺陷偵測的標準化要求。\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\",\"children\":\"如何用多酚指數評估橄欖油的健康價值？\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\",\"children\":\"▾\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\",\"children\":\"多酚指數（Polyphenol Index）是一個綜合評估框架：總酚含量（TPC）≥500mg/kg 為頂級（Premium）；250-500mg/kg 為高品質（High Quality）；100-250mg/kg 為標準品質（Standard）；<100mg/kg 多酚功效極低，不值得為健康因素溢價購買。然而，真正重要的不只是總量，而是各類多酚的比例——Oleocanthal 和 Hydroxytyrosol 的含量比整體 TPC 更能預測特定健康功效。\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\",\"children\":\"2026 年台灣市場能買到真正的高多酚橄欖油嗎？\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\",\"children\":\"▾\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\",\"children\":\"可以，但需要懂得辨識。台灣進口管道中，部分專業有機食品通路（如 Jason's、棉花田等）有進口具備 CoA 報告的高品質 EVOO。挑選要點：確認採收年份為 2025 或 2026 年（避開老油）；詢問進口商是否有多酚含量（TPC）的第三方檢驗報告；品牌認證優先選擇 NYIOOC 或 EVOOLEUM 得獎產品；預算在每瓶 NT$600-1,500 以上的進口 EVOO 較可能達到高多酚標準。\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n25:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-olive-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"📚\"}],\" 參考文獻\"]}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"text-sm text-gray-500 flex gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-olive-400 font-medium shrink-0\",\"children\":[\"[\",1,\"]\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",n